      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not assessed at MRL 2; solver error subsumed under code verification and discretization error factors.",
      "rationale": "At Model Risk Level 2, explicit quantification of numerical solver error beyond code verification and discretization convergence is not required. This factor is scoped out per the MRL 2 assessment plan."
