      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not assessed at MRL 2; analyst training and simulation protocol documentation address use error at a level commensurate with MRL 2.",
      "rationale": "MRL 2 does not mandate formal use-error quantification. Analyst qualifications are documented and simulation protocols are reviewed internally. Formal use-error assessment is deferred to higher MRL applications."
