      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not assessed at MRL 2; FDA round-robin dataset provides sufficient sample coverage for the validation comparison.",
      "rationale": "The FDA benchmark dataset encompasses measurements from multiple laboratories, providing adequate statistical coverage for MRL 2 validation. Formal sample-size analysis is not required at this risk level."
